<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <h2>About Application</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>It is ASP.NET Core MVC webapp developed following the Onion Architecture that performs CRUD on employee details</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <h2>Database</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>The database used is the  In Memory Database that is provided by the Entity Framework Core</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <h2>Check it out</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Click on employees link in the menu bar to check it or <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Employee" asp-action="Index">here</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <h2>Source Code</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>The source code to the web app can be found at my git repo <a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=518008">www.github.com/muwongeemmanuel</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
